channel.title: Comments on: With no understanding of the concept of supply and demand, Hole reunites, anyway

item.title: By: fak3r
item.dc:creator: fak3r
item.description: What a joke, I remember being surprised liking Celebrity Skin, but at the time I was visiting friends in LA and blamed that environment, but then I realized that Billy Corgan was responsible for most (all) of the pop hooks that had a hold of me. Of course then I start thinking, how did that guy make Gish and then get so washed out, but that's another comment, eh?
